## ⬇️ Installation

### Installation via Cargo

```bash
cargo add {{ package.name }}
```

### Installation in `Cargo.toml`

Enable all default features:

```toml
[dependencies]
{{ package.name }} = { version = "0.4" }
```

Enable only specific features:

```toml
[dependencies]
{{ package.name }} = { version = "0.4", default-features = false, features = ["serde"] }
```

